{B01: Scandinavian Defence} 1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Qxd5 3. Nc3 Qd6 4. d3 Nf6 5. Nf3
Bf5 (5... c6 6. g3 Bg4 7. h3 Bxf3 8. Qxf3 Nbd7 9. Bg2 e6 10. O-O Qc7 11. b3 Bd6
12. Bb2 O-O 13. Rad1 Rad8 14. Rfe1 Rfe8 15. d4 Nf8 16. Ne4 Be7 17. c4 Nxe4 18.
